s/event/4/5/a/6/600_448877830.jpeg\" /></p> <p>This place needs no introduction for the rides. It has 18 water rides and 25 dry rides. We hope it makes your experience with \'Climb on\' more enjoyable! <br/>We Brings you a special event of outplay to live your world and play it Ours. This event is about enjoying and appreciating simple adventure. Have you discovered your thrill-face yet?</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/6/2/3/600_448877955.jpeg\" /></p> <p><img src=\"http://photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/6/3/2/600_448877970.jpeg\" /></p> <p><b>Safety: </b>Wonder la is one of the only 2 amusement parks in India to implement OHSAS <b>18001:2007</b> safety standards. All attractions and components are maintained according to strict tolerances for performance. </p> <p><b>Things to bring:</b></p> <p>* Food ( you can buy in the park too) </p> <p>* Swimming tube (If needed)</p> <p>* Swim shorts</p> <p><b>Cost  :</b> Rs 650/per head  <b>[ No club fee ] </b></p> <p> which <b>doesn\'t</b> include transportation and food.</p> <p><b>Important Instructions:  </b></p> <p>1) No smoking and no alcohol <br/>2) No littering, no pollution of water <br/>3) This is leisure trip, but all care has to be taken to make your trip comfortable </p> <p><b>NOTE</b>: Please answer all the questions. </p> <p><b>Contact </b>: Suman 99660 02025</p> '),(512,'1459273810000','Rappelling, Scrambling and basic knots and Kedarnath memories','229965390','1461814415000','https://www.meetup.com/Theclimbon/events/229965390/','Contact Event Organiser: Suman 9966002025','2016-04-24 06:00:00.000000','past',' Near Raidurgam Bus stop Mumbai Highway Road ','Hyderabad','in','Khajaguda',0,'2016-04-28 03:33:00.000000','<p>Khajaguda is quality outdoor climbing locations all varying in scenery, rock quality and texture. </p> <p><img src=\"http://photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/f/0/e/600_435483854.jpeg\" /></p> <p><img src=\"http://photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/5/1/d/600_436790461.jpeg\" /></p> <p>Spend the day with our certified guide learning the basics of rock climbing and improving your top-roping skills and techniques.</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/2/d/8/a/600_432191658.jpeg\" /></p> <p><img src=\"http://photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/d/7/a/4/600_433495204.jpeg\" /></p> <p><img src=\"http://photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/9/3/2/600_436762834.jpeg\" /></p> <p>Our goal is to facilitate fun, informative, inspirational and recreational outdoor rock climbing experiences. </p> <p>Also we are expecting Kedarnath trip members to join the event and share their experience and answer our curiosity :) </p> <p><b>Basic Rappelling and Scrambling:</b></p> <p>Time : 6am  - 11:30 am</p> <p>Tee shirt</p> <p>Tracks - No shorts please. </p> <p>Shoes are a MUST</p> <p>Cap advised</p> <p>Water 2 liter</p> <p>Snacks to Fill On to Climb On.</p> <p>Cost breakup: Rs. 100/- towards Club Fund Includes Expertise[Know-how], Equipment, stationary and first-Aid.(Fuel, food, water is not included) <br/><b><br/></b></p> <p><b>Gear Provided. </b>Ropes, Carabiners, Harness and necessary equipment for climbing will be provided by our club, so leave on us.</p> <p>Meet up at Raidurgam bus-stop  near Wells Fargo at 6:00 AM. </p> <p>Join Us : <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/666901140078913/\">Facebook</a></p> '),(513,'1461149735000','Lets Play: Childhood Games @ Botanical Garden','230513010','1462040618000','https://www.meetup.com/Theclimbon/events/230513010/','ClimbOn Pallavi - 7674070563 ClimbOn Pravallika-7702523099','2016-04-30 06:00:00.000000','past','kondapur','Hyderabad','in','Botanical Garden',0,'2016-04-30 18:23:00.000000','<p>Relish your childhood fun with games like pithoo (7 Stones), langdi tang, vish amrit , kho-kho and many more…</p> <p>Timing: 6:00 AM to 9:00 AM</p> <p><b>Games: </b></p> <p>·  Kho Kho</p> <p>·  7 Stones</p> <p>·  Blindfold</p> <p>·  Langdi Tang</p> <p>·  Dog and the Bone</p>