.com/Theclimbon/events/230626075/','Contact Event Organiser:ClimbOn-Pravallika 7702523099','2016-04-30 10:45:00.000000','past','Opposite RTO Office  Raghavendra Colony, Kondapur Beside Kritunga Restaurant','Kondapur','in','Seasons Swimming Pool ',0,'2016-04-30 06:59:00.000000','<p><b>Beat the Heat at an Indoor Swimming Pool:</b></p> <p>Did you know that even a gentle swim can burn over 200 Kcal in half an hour and a fast front crawl can burn as many calories as an 8mph run? </p> <p>Exercise at a slower pace for extended periods of time. You\'ll burn more fat if you slow your speed and swim for at least 30 minutes. When you exercise at lower intensities, you burn higher percentages of fat calories.</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/4/5/4/600_447778452.jpeg\" /></p> <p><b>7 Reasons for Swimming: </b>Heart Helper, Balance Your Build, increasing muscle strength,Increased Flexibility, Strengthen Your Core,Endurance,Weight Loss.</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/e/4/5/f/600_447778463.jpeg\" /></p> <p>Swimming pools provide a great way to accomplish some aerobic exercise when it’s too hot to even think about jogging or playing a land sport. <b>Swimming provides a total body workout that exercises your arms, legs, and torso. If you’re new to exercise, swimming is a great choice because it’s low impact, fun, and a good way to get in a great workout without actually feeling like you’re working out – you’ll feel like you’re cooling down. </b></p> <p>Lets catch up for an hour long swimming meetup at Kondapur. </p> <p><b>People who are new to swimming can also join. We will provide you the basic training. </b> Depth of the pool ranges from 3 Ft to 7 Ft.</p> <p><b>Cost: Rs. 200/hr Swimming Charges</b>, which includes <b>swimming costumes (for Boys). Girls need to bring their own swimming  costumes. </b>As we would be repeating this event every week, you may go for weekend Registration to that indoor swimming pool (1200/month for weekends; including Holidays)</p> <p><b>CLUB FUND: ZERO</b></p> <p><b><br/></b></p> <p><b>Follow us on:  </b></p> <p>Meetup: <a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Theclimbon/Facebook:\"><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Theclimbon/\" class=\"linkified\">http://www.meetup.com/Theclimbon/</a></a></p> <p>Facebook: <a href=\"http://www.fb.com/climbonhikerYoutube:\">www.fb.com/climbonhiker</a></p> <p>youtube:  <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyC11AYYd3ZebzDWAqXVgHg\">www.youtube.com/channel/UCyC11AYYd3ZebzDWAqXVgHg</a></p> '),(515,'1461127451000','Rock Climbing, Scrambling at Movie towers Hill','230509704','1462161134000','https://www.meetup.com/Theclimbon/events/230509704/','Contact Event Organiser:ClimbOn-Pravallika 7702523099','2016-05-01 05:15:00.000000','past','gachibowli','Hyderabad','in','IIT circle',0,'2016-05-02 03:52:00.000000','<p>Movie towers hills is quality outdoor climbing locations all varying in scenery, rock quality and texture. </p> <p><img src=\"http://photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/2/7/7/c/600_447370108.jpeg\" /></p> <p><img src=\"http://photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/3/d/1/600_447261457.jpeg\" /></p> <p>Spend the day with our certified guide learning the basics of rock climbing.</p> <p><img src=\"http://photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/3/c/5/600_447261445.jpeg\" /></p> <p>Our goal is to facilitate fun, informative, inspirational and recreational outdoor rock climbing experiences. </p> <p><b>Basic Rappelling and Scrambling:</b></p> <p>Time : 5:30am  - 9:00 am</p> <p>Tee shirt</p> <p>Tracks - No shorts please. </p> <p>Shoes are a MUST</p> <p>Cap advised</p> <p>Water 2 liter</p> <p>Snacks to Fill On to Climb On.</p> <p>Cost breakup: Rs. 100/- towards Club Fund Includes Expertise[Know-how], Equipment, stationary and first-Aid.(Fuel, food, water is not included) <br/><b><br/></b></p> <p><b>Gear Provided. </b>Ropes, Carabiners, Harness and necessary equipment for climbing will be provided by our club, so leave on us.</p> 